          "text": "孤一怒打昏王起下祸根。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李渊",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "到后来为王我驾坐龙廷。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李渊",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "世民儿领人马把贼来平。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李渊",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "因此上为王我不得安宁。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李渊",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "去到那楼台上细问分明。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（李渊、大太监、四太监同下。）"
        }
      ],
